1
00:00:02,16 --> 00:00:04,26
Stocks and bonds are moving higher....
股票，债券今天全都上涨了…

2
00:00:04,47 --> 00:00:06,90
Why are we watching the Business Channel?
我们为什么看商业台？

3
00:00:07,17 --> 00:00:12,00
Because the other day I saw there was a stock with my initials,MEG,on it.
因为我前几天看到有支股票 是我的名字的缩写MEG

4
00:00:12,24 --> 00:00:14,97
Sometimes it takes two or three hours before it comes up again.
有时我得苦等两，三个小时 才又会再看到

5
00:00:15,18 --> 00:00:17,14
But when it does,it's exciting.
但是看到的时候蛮兴奋的

6
00:00:18,61 --> 00:00:21,31
Okay,honey,you really need a job.
蜜糖，我看你是真的需要工作

7
00:00:22,32 --> 00:00:25,12
Dad says he knows someone you can call for an interview.
摩妮卡，说到这个，爸说 他认识一个人你可以去应徵

8
00:00:25,32 --> 00:00:28,98
Right there! That's the third sign today. Right there.
那是今天的第三个预兆了 看！

9
00:00:30,09 --> 00:00:33,36
On behalf of everyone, I'd just like to say,"Huh?"
我在替在座的每一位 说一声“什么？”

10
00:00:34,13 --> 00:00:37,50
No,you just said "dad." And everywhere I go today...
因为你刚刚说了“爸” 今天我不管到什么地方去…

11
00:00:37,70 --> 00:00:40,26
... I keep getting signs telling me to go see my father.
…我都一直得到 叫我去看我爸的预兆

12
00:00:40,50 --> 00:00:43,77
Like when I was walking over here and I passed a buffet.
像我来这里的时候 我经过一个酒“吧”

13
00:00:45,71 --> 00:00:48,18
Which is my father's last name.
你们知道吗？我爸爸就姓巴

14
00:00:49,28 --> 00:00:51,11
And they were serving franks...
我爸爸的名字是法兰…

15
00:00:51,35 --> 00:00:54,34
...which is his first name minus the "s" at the end.
…而他们也有法兰克福香肠

16
00:00:55,62 --> 00:00:59,49
And there was a rotisserie with a spinning chicken.
还有一家店呢 烤架上有鸡在转的烤鸡店

17
00:00:59,69 --> 00:01:01,68
His lndian name?
他的印第安名？

18
00:01:02,56 --> 00:01:06,96
No. Because I chickened out the last time...
不是，因为我上次去见他时…

19
00:01:07,63 --> 00:01:11,19
...when I tried to meet him. So coincidences? I don't think so.
…临“机”脱逃了 我不认为哦

20
00:01:11,40 --> 00:01:13,63
-Very freaky. -Eerie.
奇哉怪哉 怪透了

21
00:01:13,87 --> 00:01:15,63
Who wants the last hamburger?
最后一个汉堡谁要？

22
00:01:15,87 --> 00:01:18,00
That's it. Now I have to go see him.
好了，够了，我非去不可了

23
00:01:18,37 --> 00:01:19,27
Why?
为什么？

24
00:01:19,47 --> 00:01:22,07
Hamburger? McDonald's?
汉堡？麦当劳？

25
00:01:22,74 --> 00:01:25,71
Old McDonald had a farm. My dad is a pharmacist.
麦老先生有块地 我爸是“低”头配药的

26
00:01:28,02 --> 00:01:29,98
The One With the Bullies
