27
00:01:35,92 --> 00:01:40,82
六人行 第2季 第21集 两个小流氓

28
00:02:15,16 --> 00:02:17,29
Man,I am so beat.
老兄，我累歪了

29
00:02:18,37 --> 00:02:20,49
You wanna forget racquetball and hang out?
我们最好别去打什么球了 留在这里混吧

30
00:02:20,74 --> 00:02:22,17
Yeah,all right.
对，好吧

31
00:02:25,41 --> 00:02:28,71
-Hey,you're in our seats. -Sorry,we didn't know.
那是我们的位置 抱歉，我们不知道

32
00:02:28,91 --> 00:02:30,47
We were sitting there.
我们本来坐那里的

33
00:02:31,05 --> 00:02:33,88
Okay. There is one more way to say it.
这还有另外一种说法

34
00:02:34,08 --> 00:02:35,67
Who knows it?
谁知道？

35
00:02:37,32 --> 00:02:41,72
-Was that supposed to be funny? -Actually,I was going for colorful.
你这是在说笑话吗？ 不，我在说多姿多采的话

36
00:02:42,09 --> 00:02:44,35
-What's with this guy? -What's with you?
这砘镌趺戳耍 你怎么了？

37
00:02:44,56 --> 00:02:46,65
Nothing. Nothing's with him.
没什么，他没怎么

38
00:02:46,86 --> 00:02:48,35
Enjoy your coffee.
请慢用咖啡

39
00:02:55,27 --> 00:02:56,86
What just happened?
发生了什么事了？

40
00:02:58,34 --> 00:03:01,71
I just took your hat. See,I can be funny too.
我刚拿了你的帽子 你看，我也能妙趣横生

41
00:03:01,94 --> 00:03:04,88
My joke is that I took your hat.
我的笑话就是拿了你的帽子

42
00:03:05,11 --> 00:03:07,27
That is funny.
那真有趣啊

43
00:03:08,38 --> 00:03:09,44
Can I have it back?
还给我，好吗？

44
00:03:17,96 --> 00:03:20,76
You know what? I think you're very funny.
你知道吗？我觉得你很风趣

45
00:03:20,96 --> 00:03:23,56
Kudos on that hat joke.
我真的好崇拜你哦

46
00:03:25,87 --> 00:03:28,86
But come on,guys, just give him back the hat.
别这样，两位 把帽子还给他嘛

47
00:03:29,44 --> 00:03:30,37
Why should we?
为什么？

48
00:03:31,57 --> 00:03:33,60
Because it's a special hat.
因为那是顶特别的帽子

49
00:03:34,71 --> 00:03:37,51
He bought it because he was feeling down one day.
有一天他的心情很不好

50
00:03:37,71 --> 00:03:38,97
So he got the hat...
所以他就买了那顶帽子…

51
00:03:39,25 --> 00:03:41,55
...to cheer himself up,you know?
…来帮自己打气

52
00:03:42,08 --> 00:03:45,31
-Chandler -Stop talking. Stop talking now.
钱德… 别说了，别再说了

53
00:03:47,09 --> 00:03:49,42
Let me get this straight. You're stealing my hat?
让我先搞清楚 你抢了我的帽子？

54
00:03:49,72 --> 00:03:50,66
You got a problem?
你看不过去吗？

55
00:03:50,93 --> 00:03:53,72
I just want to make sure we're on the same page.
不，我只是想确定 我们大家互相了解

56
00:03:56,66 --> 00:03:58,39
How'd the interview go?
面试结果怎么样？

57
00:03:58,77 --> 00:03:59,82
It bit.
逊毙了

58
00:04:01,17 --> 00:04:03,16
It was a 50s theme restaurant.
那是一家50年代主题的餐厅

59
00:04:03,47 --> 00:04:06,93
I'd have to cook in a costume and dance on the counter.
我得穿戏服做菜在柜台上跳舞

60
00:04:07,28 --> 00:04:09,87
I was a sous chef at Cafe des Artistes.
我以前是艺术家餐厅的主厨

61
00:04:10,08 --> 00:04:14,07
How can I take a job where I have to make Laverne-and-Curly Fries?
我是说，我怎能接受一个 我得做QQ脆薯的工作呢

62
00:04:14,68 --> 00:04:16,58
-Don't do it. -How can I not do it?
那就别做啊 我怎么能不做呢？

63
00:04:16,82 --> 00:04:18,58
I have $127 in the bank!
我银行里面只剩下127块了

64
00:04:18,85 --> 00:04:21,79
Monica,relax. Go get a beer.
摩妮卡，放轻松，去拿瓶啤酒

65
00:04:21,99 --> 00:04:23,29
I don't want a beer.
我不想喝啤酒

66
00:04:23,49 --> 00:04:24,96
Who said it was for you?
谁说是给你的？

67
00:04:33,67 --> 00:04:34,97
What's the matter?
你们两个怎么了？

68
00:04:35,17 --> 00:04:38,30
Some mean guys at the coffeehouse took my hat.
咖啡厅里 有个恶汉抢了我的帽子

69
00:04:38,61 --> 00:04:40,30
-No! -You're kidding?
不会吧 你开玩笑？

70
00:04:40,51 --> 00:04:42,98
It was ridiculous. These guys were bullies.
简直荒唐透了 这些人是霸王

71
00:04:43,18 --> 00:04:45,15
Actual bullies.
是真正的霸王

72
00:04:45,35 --> 00:04:49,28
We're grownups. This kind of stuff isn't supposed to happen anymore.
你看，我们是大人了 我们不该会再碰上这种事了

73
00:04:52,32 --> 00:04:54,88
Oh,no,wait a minute. I have no one.
不，等一下，我孤家寡人

74
00:04:58,69 --> 00:05:01,22
Let's go down there and get your hat back.
我们应该过去把帽子给拿回来

75
00:05:01,53 --> 00:05:05,63
Forget it. It's probably stripped and sold for parts by now.
算了吧，说不定 已经被拆成零件给卖掉了

76
00:05:07,97 --> 00:05:09,73
-I went up! -What?
我涨了 什么？

77
00:05:10,00 --> 00:05:13,24
My stock,MEG,it went up two points.
我的股票MEG，涨了两点

78
00:05:13,47 --> 00:05:17,67
Do you realize that if I'd invested my $127 in myself yesterday...
若我昨天把我的127元 投资在我自己身上…

79
00:05:17,88 --> 00:05:21,65
...that l'd,like,have a lot more than that today.
…那我就会比我今天有钱了

80
00:05:22,92 --> 00:05:24,68
You know what? I'm going to do it.
知道吗？我要放手一搏

81
00:05:25,65 --> 00:05:27,85
-Do what? -Put all my money in me.
搏什么？ 拿钱投资我

82
00:05:28,06 --> 00:05:30,89
You don't know a thing about the stock market.
摩妮卡，你在鬼扯什么？ 你对股市一窍不通

83
00:05:31,09 --> 00:05:34,22
What's to know? Buy,sell. High,low. Bears,bulls.
要通什么？ 买，卖，高，低，空头，多头

84
00:05:34,43 --> 00:05:35,69
Yes,Manhattan.
喂，曼哈顿

85
00:05:36,50 --> 00:05:38,69
Telephone number for the stock...
麻烦帮我查一下股票…

86
00:05:39,17 --> 00:05:40,93
...selling store.
…商店

87
00:05:51,45 --> 00:05:54,28
See? I told you these pillows would be a good idea.
你看 我说应该带枕头来是对的吧

88
00:05:54,95 --> 00:05:56,04
Oh,God.
天啊

89
00:05:56,95 --> 00:05:58,11
Here we go.
就这样了

90
00:05:59,25 --> 00:06:02,85
For the first time in my life, I'm gonna say,"Hi,Birth Father!"
我就要说出我这辈子的 第一声“嗨，生父”了

91
00:06:03,79 --> 00:06:05,42
-We love you. We're here for you. -Good luck.
我们爱你，我们支持你 一切顺利

92
00:06:05,69 --> 00:06:06,85
Thanks.
谢谢

93
00:06:10,77 --> 00:06:13,13
Hey,Rach,you want some sandwich?
瑞秋，要不要三明治？

94
00:06:13,37 --> 00:06:14,89
What is in that?
里面有什么？

95
00:06:15,10 --> 00:06:17,26
Olive loaf and ham spread. No mayo.
橄榄酱，火腿酱，没美乃滋

96
00:06:17,54 --> 00:06:20,41
No,because mayo, that would make it gross.
不…再加美乃滋就恶心了

97
00:06:24,55 --> 00:06:27,07
-Run,Phoebe,run! -No,no,doggy,please!
跑，菲比，跑… 不要，狗狗，拜托

98
00:06:27,28 --> 00:06:30,88
I do so want to love all animals. Please,no. Back off!
我爱所有的动物 给它骨头，拿骨头来

99
00:06:31,15 --> 00:06:33,21
-You got a bone? -Are you kidding?
有没有骨头？ 开什么玩笑？

100
00:06:33,42 --> 00:06:35,62
Look,kibbles! Bits!
看…

101
00:06:36,56 --> 00:06:39,79
Get the hell off my leg, you yippity piece of crap!
放开我 你这只烂东西

102
00:06:46,90 --> 00:06:49,30
Okay. All right. We have a problem.
好了，我们碰上难题了

103
00:06:49,90 --> 00:06:52,40
Why don't you take his trampoline?
你为什么不拿他的弹簧垫？

104
00:06:53,01 --> 00:06:55,00
Okay,here,I know what we can do.
我知道怎么办了

105
00:06:57,41 --> 00:07:00,44
Okay,doggy,get the sandwich!
狗狗，去检三明治

106
00:07:00,92 --> 00:07:04,44
Go get the sandwich! Good doggy. Get the sandwich!
去检三明治啊，快点

107
00:07:05,09 --> 00:07:08,68
The dog will lick himself but he will not touch your sandwich.
乔伊，它宁可舔自己 也不碰你的三明治

108
00:07:08,99 --> 00:07:10,42
What does that tell you?
那告诉你什么？

109
00:07:11,36 --> 00:07:15,09
-lf he's not going to eat it,I will. -Are you crazy?
它不吃的话，我自己吃 你疯了你？

110
00:07:15,30 --> 00:07:16,96
He's just a little dog.
它是小狗而已

111
00:07:24,21 --> 00:07:25,33
-Hey. -What?
嘿 干嘛？

112
00:07:26,17 --> 00:07:28,97
Do you have to be a Century 21 real-estate agent...
你一定要当房地产经纪人…

113
00:07:29,18 --> 00:07:31,51
...to get to wear those cool jackets?
…才能穿着那么酷的外套吗？

114
00:07:33,65 --> 00:07:36,34
Do you say this stuff to girls?
你会跟女生这样搭讪吗？

115
00:07:39,05 --> 00:07:42,15
Isn't that the guy who used to wear your hat?
那不是你帽子的旧主人吗？

116
00:07:42,39 --> 00:07:44,22
And look where they're sitting.
看他们坐在哪里了

117
00:07:47,20 --> 00:07:51,53
You're joking,right? You guys just walked through the door.
你在说笑吧？你们才刚进门

118
00:07:51,80 --> 00:07:53,99
Maybe we didn't make it clear enough.
或许我们说得不够清楚

119
00:07:54,20 --> 00:07:56,83
This couch belongs to us.
这个沙发是我们的

120
00:07:57,07 --> 00:08:00,17
I'll tell you what, you call the couch...
这样吧，你们叫一声沙发…

121
00:08:00,81 --> 00:08:03,14
...and then we'll call the couch...
…然后我们也对着它叫一声…

122
00:08:04,81 --> 00:08:07,18
...and we'll see who it comes to.
…看它会到谁那里去

123
00:08:07,98 --> 00:08:11,68
You know,I keep wondering why you two are still sitting here.
我一直不懂 你们为什么还赖在这个地方？

124
00:08:11,89 --> 00:08:13,22
All right,that's it.
好了，够了

125
00:08:14,16 --> 00:08:15,88
I have had enough of this.
我受够这些狗屁了，好吗？

126
00:08:16,42 --> 00:08:17,41
Gunther.
阿刚

127
00:08:18,86 --> 00:08:21,56
These guys are trying to take our seat.
这两个砘 想抢我们的座位

128
00:08:22,76 --> 00:08:24,99
Fellas,these guys were here first.
两位，他们先来的

129
00:08:25,23 --> 00:08:27,06
Oh,sorry,didn't realize.
抱歉，我们不知道

130
00:08:27,50 --> 00:08:28,53
There you go.
好了

131
00:08:28,74 --> 00:08:30,73
Thank you,Gunther.
谢谢，阿刚

132
00:08:33,74 --> 00:08:36,40
We didn't want to have to go and do that.
是你们逼我们这么做的

133
00:08:37,01 --> 00:08:39,07
He told on us?
他打小报告？

134
00:08:39,58 --> 00:08:40,77
You told on us?
你打小报告？

135
00:08:41,02 --> 00:08:44,28
Well,pal,you didn't give me much of a choice.
兄弟，你们逼得我别无选择

136
00:08:45,79 --> 00:08:48,05
-Don't play with his thing. -I know.
别玩他的东西 我知道

137
00:08:50,42 --> 00:08:51,41
All right.
很好，我们到外面解决

138
00:08:52,29 --> 00:08:54,06
Let's take this outside.
我们到外面解决

139
00:08:56,46 --> 00:08:59,70
"Let's take this outside?"
“我们到外面解决”

140
00:09:02,10 --> 00:09:04,30
Who talks like that?
谁会这么说？

141
00:09:04,61 --> 00:09:08,94
The guy who's about to kick your ass talks like that.
即将要痛扁你们的人会这么说

142
00:09:09,21 --> 00:09:10,77
You had to ask.
谁叫你多嘴呢

143
00:09:14,55 --> 00:09:16,88
Okay,okay,look. See...
好吧…

144
00:09:17,15 --> 00:09:21,14
...the thing is,we're not gonna fight you guys.
…我们不想用武力来解决

145
00:09:22,32 --> 00:09:23,52
Here's the deal.
那么这样好了

146
00:09:23,72 --> 00:09:28,66
You won't have to,so long as you never ever show your faces here again.
你们保证从今以后 不踏入这家咖啡厅

147
00:09:34,10 --> 00:09:36,83
I think you played the Gunther card too soon.
你太早把阿刚抬出来了吧

148
00:09:43,18 --> 00:09:45,44
Hey,Pheebs,I think you're good to go.
菲菲，我想你可以上去了

149
00:09:46,11 --> 00:09:47,34
Yeah,I don't know.
我不知道

150
00:09:49,35 --> 00:09:50,48
What's the matter?
又怎么了？

151
00:09:50,69 --> 00:09:53,52
I just think that this was a really bad sign.
我是觉得这是个很不好的预兆

152
00:09:53,75 --> 00:09:56,78
Like the beast at the threshold.
我是说像门槛上的野兽啦

153
00:09:58,26 --> 00:10:03,09
It's just I have no family left, except for my grandmother.
我已经没有别的亲人了 除了我奶奶之外

154
00:10:03,33 --> 00:10:06,32
But let's face it,she's not gonna be around forever.
可是面对现实吧 她又不会永远都活着

155
00:10:06,53 --> 00:10:07,97
Despite what she says.
不管怎么说

156
00:10:09,64 --> 00:10:14,57
And I have a sister who I've barely spoken to since we shared a womb.
我有个除了在子宫里面 几乎没有说过话的姐姐

157
00:10:15,94 --> 00:10:17,97
I don't know. This is my real father...
这是我真正的父亲…

158
00:10:18,21 --> 00:10:21,55
...and I want things to be, like,just right.
…我只是要一切完美嘛

159
00:10:21,78 --> 00:10:23,37
I completely understand.
我完全了解

160
00:10:23,65 --> 00:10:24,78
Whatever you need.
对，随你要怎么样

161
00:10:26,35 --> 00:10:28,12
Hey,you want to go home?
你要回家吗？

162
00:10:28,39 --> 00:10:30,62
Okay,thanks. Sorry,again.
谢了，对不起

163
00:10:50,04 --> 00:10:51,71
What was that?
那是什么？

164
00:10:56,05 --> 00:10:58,88
I'm guessing the threshold's clear now.
我猜现在门槛没有狗了

165
00:11:03,02 --> 00:11:05,36
I want to buy five shares of SGJ. Now.
我要买五股XTJ 我现在就要

166
00:11:05,59 --> 00:11:07,93
Come on,time is money,my friend!
快点，时间就是金钱

167
00:11:08,30 --> 00:11:09,39
Thank you!
谢谢

168
00:11:11,27 --> 00:11:13,20
"Time is money,my friend?"
“时间就是金钱”？

169
00:11:13,40 --> 00:11:15,53
You missed "Takes money to make money"...
“时间就是金钱”…

170
00:11:15,74 --> 00:11:19,70
...and "Don't make me come down there and kick your Wall Street butt."
…还有，“别逼我 过去踢你的华尔街屁股”

171
00:11:20,31 --> 00:11:23,71
I made $ 17 before breakfast. What have you done?
我早餐前就赚了十七块耶 那你做了什么？

172
00:11:23,91 --> 00:11:27,54
I had breakfast here, so technically I saved $3.50.
我早餐在这个地方吃的 所以技术上我省了三块半

173
00:11:28,98 --> 00:11:30,45
How did you make $17?
你怎么赚十七块的？

174
00:11:30,65 --> 00:11:32,95
Well,my financially challenged friends...
我的经济白痴朋友…

175
00:11:33,25 --> 00:11:36,49
...I split my money and I bought some shares of CHP and ZXY.
…我用我的钱分别买了些 CHP跟ZXY股

176
00:11:37,46 --> 00:11:38,65
How come those?
你怎么选的？

177
00:11:38,93 --> 00:11:43,45
Well,CHP because I used to have a crush on Erik Estrada.
CHP是因为我暗恋过 “加州公路巡警”的奇普

178
00:11:44,60 --> 00:11:48,00
And ZXY because I think it sounds "zexy."
ZXY 那是听起来很“劲”感啊

179
00:11:48,97 --> 00:11:50,96
What happened to MEG?
那你的…MEG呢？

180
00:11:51,17 --> 00:11:53,61
MEG was good for me,but I dumped her.
MEG帮我赚过钱 但是被我甩了

181
00:11:53,91 --> 00:11:57,00
My motto is,"Get out before they go down."
我的座右铭 是在“疲软”以前出场的

182
00:11:58,35 --> 00:12:01,25
That is so not my motto.
这倒不是我的作风

183
00:12:07,86 --> 00:12:08,95
How's the dog?
狗好点了没？

184
00:12:09,19 --> 00:12:12,65
Okay. I talked to the vet. People are so nice upstate.
我跟兽医谈好了 纽约州的人真好

185
00:12:12,86 --> 00:12:16,49
He said the little fella's gonna be okay,and I can get him tomorrow.
他说那个小砘锊换嵊形侍 明天我可以去接它了

186
00:12:16,70 --> 00:12:18,32
-Good. -Thank God.
好，好极了 谢天谢地

187
00:12:18,53 --> 00:12:21,30
But he did have to have a bunch of stitches.
可是他必须帮它缝好多针

188
00:12:21,50 --> 00:12:25,53
And he said that only once in a blue moon does a dog's ear grow back.
而且他还说除非天下红雨 狗才会再长出耳朵来的

189
00:12:26,11 --> 00:12:28,27
So still hoping.
所以还有一点点希望

190
00:12:30,68 --> 00:12:35,51
Now are you going to call your dad to let him know that his dog is okay?
那你现在要打电话告诉你爸 他的狗没事了吗？

191
00:12:35,88 --> 00:12:39,38
I don't want to meet my father over the phone.
我不想在电话上跟我爸相认

192
00:12:39,65 --> 00:12:42,18
What will I say, "Hi,I'm the daughter you abandoned.
我该跟他先什么呢？ “我是菲比被你抛弃的女儿”

193
00:12:42,46 --> 00:12:44,95
Oh,by the way,I broke your dog."
“对了，我撞伤了你的狗”

194
00:12:46,06 --> 00:12:48,55
Hey,Pheebs,if you want,I'll do it.
菲菲，我可以帮你打的

195
00:12:50,56 --> 00:12:54,13
Listen,just don't say anything about me,okay?
听着，拜托千万不要提我的事

196
00:12:54,84 --> 00:12:55,86
Don't...
别…

197
00:12:57,97 --> 00:13:00,00
... be too long with the phone.
…讲电话太久

198
00:13:00,84 --> 00:13:04,00
She'll be a much better friend once the market closes.
股市收盘以后 她会是个比较好的朋友

199
00:13:06,98 --> 00:13:07,81
It's a woman.
是个女的

200
00:13:08,18 --> 00:13:09,48
So talk to her.
你跟她讲啊

201
00:13:13,02 --> 00:13:14,39
Hello,Mrs. Buffay.
巴太太

202
00:13:16,09 --> 00:13:18,39
I know where your dog is.
我知道你的狗在哪里

203
00:13:19,23 --> 00:13:23,82
I want you to know he'll be returned to you almost as good as new...
我要你知道 我们会在24小时之内…

204
00:13:24,06 --> 00:13:25,86
...within 24 hours.
…将它几乎完好如初的还给你

205
00:13:26,07 --> 00:13:27,56
Goodbye.
再见

206
00:13:34,44 --> 00:13:36,50
-Why the voice? -Hard to say.
干嘛装声音？ 很难讲

207
00:13:40,21 --> 00:13:41,51
Your cappuccino,sir.
你的卡布基诺来了

208
00:13:41,72 --> 00:13:43,01
Thank you.
谢谢

209
00:13:46,45 --> 00:13:49,85
-This is better than the coffeehouse. -Absolutely.
在这里喝比在咖啡厅好多了 对极了

210
00:13:58,90 --> 00:14:01,37
How come it's not mixing with the water?
咖啡粉为什么不化？

211
00:14:01,57 --> 00:14:04,04
The package says to keep it moving.
包装上说你必须要不断的搅拌

212
00:14:04,27 --> 00:14:06,64
Stir and drink,never let it settle.
搅拌，喝 别让咖啡停下来

213
00:14:12,21 --> 00:14:14,04
This is ridiculous.
这太荒唐了吧

214
00:14:14,25 --> 00:14:16,98
After I get back from my niece's christening...
这样吧，等我从 外甥女的洗礼回来之后呢…

215
00:14:17,22 --> 00:14:21,59
...I'll go to the coffeehouse with you and we'll have a cup of coffee.
…我陪你们两个到中央公园去 我们好好的享受一杯咖啡

216
00:14:21,82 --> 00:14:24,26
No problem. Joey's there.
没问题的，有乔伊在

217
00:14:29,30 --> 00:14:34,23
I don't want to have to have Joey with me every time I want decent coffee.
不，我不希望每一次 我想喝一杯好咖啡

218
00:14:34,57 --> 00:14:38,06
And I don't want to drink cappuccino with a "k."
我也不想一辈子 喝这个牌子的泡沫咖啡

219
00:14:38,31 --> 00:14:41,40
I say you and I go and stand up to those guys.
我认为我们应该回咖啡厅去 勇敢的面对那些人

220
00:14:41,61 --> 00:14:44,08
All right,hang on a second there,Custer.
好吧，你先等一等，将军

221
00:14:45,61 --> 00:14:48,08
Ross,have you ever been beaten up before?
真的，罗斯 你以前有没有被扁过？

222
00:14:48,28 --> 00:14:49,25
Yeah,sure.
有啊，当然有

223
00:14:49,65 --> 00:14:52,24
By someone besides Monica?
被摩妮卡以外的人？ 没有

224
00:14:53,52 --> 00:14:54,38
So what?
所以呢？

225
00:14:54,59 --> 00:14:58,62
So we get beaten up. Maybe that's something a man has to go through.
就算被扁又怎么样？也许每个 男人都得经历过一次这个…

226
00:14:58,83 --> 00:15:01,82
Like a rite of passage or something.
成人式之类什么的

227
00:15:02,10 --> 00:15:05,12
Couldn't we just lose our virginities again?
不能再失去一次童贞就好吗？

228
00:15:06,27 --> 00:15:09,03
Because I think actually mine's growing back.
因为我想我的又长回来了

229
00:15:11,37 --> 00:15:13,53
-I need $100. -What?
我需要借100 什么？

230
00:15:13,77 --> 00:15:15,37
Welcome home.
欢迎光临

231
00:15:16,01 --> 00:15:17,44
-I need $100. -For what?
我需要借一百块 干嘛？

232
00:15:17,65 --> 00:15:20,14
-To get back in the game. -When did you get out?
我得回到场上玩 你什么时候退场的？

233
00:15:20,35 --> 00:15:23,11
I lost it all. I lost it.
不知道，我赔光了

234
00:15:23,48 --> 00:15:26,72
I've come to terms with it, you have to,too.
我接受事实了，你也得这样

235
00:15:29,66 --> 00:15:33,02
Look,Mon,I'm really sorry.
听着，摩妮卡，我很遗撼

236
00:15:33,23 --> 00:15:34,96
Where are we on the $100?
你到底借不借？

237
00:15:35,16 --> 00:15:36,36
I don't have it.
我没钱啊

238
00:15:36,56 --> 00:15:38,16
But I need it!
可是我需要

239
00:15:39,00 --> 00:15:41,43
Otherwise,I'll have to take that diner job.
那我得去那个烂馆子工作了

240
00:15:41,64 --> 00:15:45,83
You know,with the dancing and the costumes.
你知道的 就是跳舞还有穿戏服

241
00:15:49,01 --> 00:15:52,14
I don't want to have to wear flame-retardant boobs.
我不想穿 连火都烧不着的假胸部

242
00:15:53,25 --> 00:15:55,81
Nobody does,honey.
没人想，蜜糖

243
00:15:59,75 --> 00:16:01,02
Noodle!
面面

244
00:16:01,22 --> 00:16:05,66
Oh,my God. What the hell happened to my dog?
老天啊，我的狗到底怎么了？

245
00:16:05,89 --> 00:16:07,02
It was an accident.
那是个意外

246
00:16:07,23 --> 00:16:10,56
And the woman who did this would never hurt a dog on purpose.
而且那个肇事的女人 绝不会蓄意伤害一只狗的

247
00:16:10,76 --> 00:16:12,43
She's a vegetarian.
她吃素

248
00:16:13,77 --> 00:16:14,93
Are these stitches?
这是什么？缝线？

249
00:16:15,17 --> 00:16:18,76
Yeah,eight of them. That's 56 to him.
对，八针 对狗来说是56针啦

250
00:16:19,67 --> 00:16:22,40
If it's raining,you can't let him look up...
还有，下雨的时候…

251
00:16:22,68 --> 00:16:24,84
... because that cone will fill up fast.
…不要让它抬头太久 因为那玩意儿装不了多少水的

252
00:16:26,71 --> 00:16:28,41
Thanks for bringing back what's left of him.
谢谢你送它的残骸回来

253
00:16:28,62 --> 00:16:31,74
-ls Frank home? -How do you know Frank?
没问题，法兰在吗？ 你怎么认识他的？

254
00:16:31,95 --> 00:16:35,01
Just from a long time ago. Is he here?
那是很久以前的事，他在吗？

255
00:16:40,86 --> 00:16:41,85
What?
什么事啊？

256
00:16:43,93 --> 00:16:45,36
I mean Frank Senior.
我是说，老的法兰

257
00:16:45,57 --> 00:16:47,30
He went out for groceries.
他去买日用品了

258
00:16:47,53 --> 00:16:48,80
Will he be back soon?
他很快回来吗？

259
00:16:49,27 --> 00:16:52,64
He left four years ago. We're expecting him back any minute.
他四年前去的 所以我们猜他随时会回来

260
00:16:54,98 --> 00:16:56,10
I'm gonna go.
那我要走了

261
00:16:56,31 --> 00:16:58,61
I'm sorry about the dog. Everything.
对不起，关于… 关于那只狗

262
00:16:58,88 --> 00:16:59,90
I'm sorry.
对不起

263
00:17:00,65 --> 00:17:01,71
Hey,lady!
小姐

264
00:17:02,15 --> 00:17:03,81
Hey,wait up!
等一下

265
00:17:08,49 --> 00:17:12,08
-How do you know my dad? -Well,I don't really.
你怎么认识我老爸的？ 我不认识他

266
00:17:12,29 --> 00:17:15,09
Just genetically.
基因上认得

267
00:17:15,63 --> 00:17:17,89
He's kind of my dad too.
他也算是我老爸吧

268
00:17:18,40 --> 00:17:19,39
Heavy.
不得了

269
00:17:21,84 --> 00:17:25,57
So did he ever talk about me... Phoebe?
他有没有提过我…菲比？

270
00:17:25,77 --> 00:17:28,33
No,but he didn't really talk about anything.
没有，不过他一向沉默是金啦

271
00:17:30,58 --> 00:17:32,14
Except stilts.
除了高~

272
00:17:33,11 --> 00:17:35,64
-Stilts? -Yeah,he loved stilts.
高~？ 对啊，他爱高~

273
00:17:35,85 --> 00:17:39,81
One time,I was upstairs stealing cigarettes out of my mom's purse...
有一次我在楼上，正在偷 我妈皮包里面的香烟时…

274
00:17:40,42 --> 00:17:42,79
...and all of a sudden I look over...
…突然间我张望了一下…

275
00:17:43,02 --> 00:17:45,86
...and there's Dad's head, bobbing past the window.
…看到我爸的头从窗外经过

276
00:17:47,69 --> 00:17:50,69
He just had this big smile on his face and he was waving...
他脸上满是笑意地 向我挥了一挥手…

277
00:17:50,96 --> 00:17:53,80
...because he was happiest when he was on his stilts.
…因为他踩高~的时候 就是他最高兴的时候了

278
00:17:58,44 --> 00:18:00,37
I don't know what to do with that.
我根本不会踩那玩意儿

279
00:18:00,71 --> 00:18:02,11
Me neither.
我也是

280
00:18:05,48 --> 00:18:07,95
So are you,like,my big sister?
所以你是我姐姐？

281
00:18:08,95 --> 00:18:11,65
This is huge. You can buy me beer!
真不得了，你可以请我喝啤酒

282
00:18:12,85 --> 00:18:13,95
I'm not gonna.
我不要

283
00:18:15,19 --> 00:18:18,89
But you know what's cool? If you had a friend named Pete,I could say...
知道怎么样最酷吗？ 如果你有个朋友叫做彼得…

284
00:18:19,16 --> 00:18:21,72
... "I know Pete. He's friends with my brother."
…那我就可说“彼得，我认得 他是我弟弟的朋友”

285
00:18:22,46 --> 00:18:25,33
-I got a friend named Mark. -That'll work too.
我有个朋友叫马克 那也可以啊

286
00:18:25,57 --> 00:18:26,40
Cool. All right.
酷，好

287
00:18:27,50 --> 00:18:31,56
So maybe,you know, I could give you a call sometime.
或许改天我可以打个电话给你

288
00:18:32,51 --> 00:18:34,13
We could talk or something.
我们可以好好聊聊或什么的

289
00:18:34,37 --> 00:18:36,67
-Yeah,that'd be okay. -All right.
好啊，那会很好 好

290
00:18:36,88 --> 00:18:38,50
I'm in the book.
电话簿上有我的电话

291
00:18:43,15 --> 00:18:45,14
So stilts,huh?
那…高~？

292
00:18:45,85 --> 00:18:50,22
If you want,I can show you where he hit his head on the rain gutter.
你要的话，我可以带你去看 他头撞到排水管的那个地方

293
00:18:55,03 --> 00:18:58,90
We did it. We're here. We are standing our ground.
我们办到了，我们在这儿 我们坚守我们的立场

294
00:19:00,57 --> 00:19:03,90
-How long does coffee take? -Would you come on? Come on!
一杯咖啡到底要煮多久？ 快点？快点呀

295
00:19:05,94 --> 00:19:07,07
Thank you.
谢谢

296
00:19:18,55 --> 00:19:20,95
-There we go. -I think we proved our point.
好了，喝完了 我想我们证明了

297
00:19:23,22 --> 00:19:25,89
-You burn your mouth? -Cannot feel my tongue.
烫到嘴了没有？ 舌头没感觉了

298
00:19:30,56 --> 00:19:32,12
Bullies! Big bullies!
霸王，大霸王

299
00:19:32,70 --> 00:19:35,86
Look who's here. It's the weenies.
看看谁来了？是胆小鬼们

300
00:19:37,54 --> 00:19:40,27
Did we not make ourselves clear the other day?
我们那天讲得不够清楚 是不是？

301
00:19:40,47 --> 00:19:41,87
That's why we're here.
所以我们才来

302
00:19:42,11 --> 00:19:44,41
Yes,we're standing our ground.
对，我们在坚守立场

303
00:19:44,95 --> 00:19:46,78
Apparently.
你也看的出来吧

304
00:19:47,11 --> 00:19:48,64
Let's do this already.
少说废话了

305
00:19:48,92 --> 00:19:49,94
You got a weapon?
你那是什么？武器？

306
00:19:51,12 --> 00:19:53,92
A nice watch. I don't want to break it on your ribs.
一只好表 我不想在槌你的时候弄坏它

307
00:19:54,12 --> 00:19:55,38
All right,let's do this.
来吧，来呀

308
00:19:57,16 --> 00:20:01,79
Question: If I don't care about my watch,can I use it as a weapon?
我有问题，若我不在乎我的表 我可以拿下来当武器吗？

309
00:20:02,06 --> 00:20:04,16
-What do you mean? -It's sharp,it's metal.
什么意思？ 这很利，是金属做的

310
00:20:04,43 --> 00:20:07,26
I think I can do some serious damage with it.
我想这可以用来 发挥很大的杀伤力

311
00:20:08,00 --> 00:20:09,83
No,you can't use your watch.
不，你不能用手表

312
00:20:11,44 --> 00:20:13,17
Or your keys.
或钥匙

313
00:20:13,94 --> 00:20:15,34
Here's what we'll do.
听我说，这样好了

314
00:20:15,64 --> 00:20:19,08
We'll put all keys and watches in the hat over there.
把所有的钥匙和手表 都放在这个帽子里面摆在那里

315
00:20:19,48 --> 00:20:20,50
All right?
好吗？

316
00:20:22,52 --> 00:20:25,01
All right,come on,man. Let's do it!
好了，来吧…

317
00:20:25,32 --> 00:20:28,81
Before I forget,are we hitting faces?
趁我还记得，脸可以打吗？

318
00:20:29,12 --> 00:20:30,92
Of course. Why wouldn't you hit faces?
当然可以打，脸为何不能打？

319
00:20:31,16 --> 00:20:34,42
I have to work on Monday. I have a big presentation.
因为我星期一还得上班 我得上台说话

320
00:20:35,66 --> 00:20:38,63
Actually,I gotta show this apartment tomorrow...
我明天要带人去看房子…

321
00:20:38,87 --> 00:20:42,16
...and this no-faces thing might not be a bad idea.
…所以不打脸这码子事 倒是满好的主意

322
00:20:43,44 --> 00:20:44,77
Nothing from the neck up.
脖子以上不准打

323
00:20:46,71 --> 00:20:48,37
Or the waist down.
或腰部以下

324
00:20:49,31 --> 00:20:52,14
-Dana's ovulating. -Really? You guys trying again?
黛娜在排卵期 真的？你们又在试了？

325
00:20:53,48 --> 00:20:56,54
Let me get this straight. We're talking about the middle?
好吧，让我先搞清楚 我们只能够打中间的部份吗？

326
00:20:56,78 --> 00:20:57,68
Come on!
来呀

327
00:20:58,05 --> 00:21:01,71
You want a piece of this? I'm standing here!
你们要打这边？还是打这边？

328
00:21:03,56 --> 00:21:05,55
Those guys are taking our stuff!
你们看，我们东西被偷了

329
00:21:10,50 --> 00:21:12,83
God,that was amazing. That was incredible.
天啊，那真是不可思

330
00:21:13,07 --> 00:21:15,97
-You guys kicked butt! -Us? What about you guys?
你们好厉害 我们？那你们呢？

331
00:21:16,17 --> 00:21:18,97
You really gave it to old Mr. Clean back there.
你们真的 给了那个老贼颜色瞧了

332
00:21:19,24 --> 00:21:21,97
-He was a big guy. -Yeah,he was,wasn't he?
那砘锍さ煤米嘲 没错，不是吗？

333
00:21:22,18 --> 00:21:24,17
I wouldn't know, having missed everything.
是呀，我不知道，我全错过了

334
00:21:24,48 --> 00:21:26,50
Don't do that to yourself.
不要太苛责自己了

335
00:21:26,71 --> 00:21:30,55
Any one of us could have tripped over that little girl's jump rope.
